data.description: Welcome Home to 397 Chemistry Circle! This 4-bedroom residence located in The Reserve at Eagle run is conveniently located near award winning DD2 Schools. Embrace sustainable living and enjoy the long-term energy savings with Solar Panels! Enjoy the abundant natural light that streams in the heart of the home! The eat in gourmet kitchen features 42'' cabinets, stainless steel appliances and a large walk in pantry. Close by is the formal dining room that is great for hosting holiday gatherings.Just off the entrance is an office/flex space to use how you choose. Upstairs are 3 generously sized bedrooms which provide ample space for rest and relaxation along with the Owners Suite where you can enjoy the luxury of a private retreat with an upstairs porch to enjoy your morning coffee. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own!
